definitions.definition: A fabric , usually of thick cotton or wool , having a dull brownish yellow , dull grey , or dun colour .
Often in the plural form drabs : apparel , especially trousers , made from this fabric.
( by extension ) A dull or uninteresting appearance or situation , unremarkable .

main_definition: A fabric , usually of thick cotton or wool , having a dull brownish yellow , dull grey , or dun colour .

definitions.definition: ( dated ) A dirty or untidy woman ; a slattern .
( dated ) A promiscuous woman, a slut ; a prostitute .

definitions.definition: A small amount , especially of money .

definitions.definition: A box used in a saltworks for holding the salt when taken out of the boiling pans .

definitions.definition: ( chiefly transgender slang ) An instance of a transgender or non-binary person presenting as the gender corresponding to their sex assigned at birth instead of that corresponding to their internal gender identity (most commonly a trans woman dressed as a man ).
